    "answer_id" : 55509285,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I've just had a similar issue. The project had opened using Java 9 but even after all the modules and project were set back to 1.8, I was still getting the error. </p>\n\n<p>I needed to force Gradle to refresh the project and then everything ran as expected. </p>\n"
