    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>Gradle</strong>\nI had the same issue and changing all the settings given in the earlier solutions made no difference. Than I went to the build.gradle and found this line and deleted it.</p>\n\n<pre><code>sourceCompatibility = '11'\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and it worked! :)</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 17633794,
      "reputation" : 43,
      "user_id" : 12797415,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/hOEZP.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Lucian L.",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/12797415/lucian-l"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1580222956,
    "creation_date" : 1580222956,
    "answer_id" : 59951331,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In <strong>Project Structure</strong> in <strong>Project SDK:</strong> modify SDK to 11 or higher and in <strong>Project language level:</strong> modify to 11 - Local variable syntax for lambda parameters</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2349225,
      "reputation" : 27306,
      "user_id" : 2058547,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 60,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/NiRyA.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Ojonugwa Jude Ochalifu",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2058547/ojonugwa-jude-ochalifu"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 4,
    "last_activity_date" : 1596373002,
    "creation_date" : 1596373002,
    "answer_id" : 63216255,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was having this issue while running a SpringBoot project (Maven)</p>\n<p>In my POM file I changed the java version from 11 to 8 and it worked:</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;java.version&gt;8&lt;/java.version&gt; //The default was 11\n&lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Make sure to <code>Load maven changes</code> else the change won't reflect.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 18503839,
      "reputation" : 85,
      "user_id" : 13480575,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/kSz0t.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "shubham",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/13480575/shubham"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1600148953,
    "creation_date" : 1600148953,
    "answer_id" : 63895852,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just additional note:</p>\n<p>when you creating a new project from start.spring.io make sure you select your JDK version theirs by default is set to JDK 11, later it will cause the above issue.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 18759194,
      "reputation" : 1322,
      "user_id" : 13678514,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AOh14GgXCLwvp_xlyRiINFAEIItN4QhZlyCJyf-4ZpDE=k-s256",
      "display_name" : "Emmanuel Njorodongo",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/13678514/emmanuel-njorodongo"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1622190959,
    "creation_date" : 1622190959,
    "answer_id" : 67735564,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>File &gt; Project Structure &gt; Project &gt; Project SDK &gt; Choose Version\nFile &gt; Project Structure &gt; Project &gt; Project Language Level &gt; Choose Version\nFile &gt; Project Structure &gt; Modules &gt; Sources Tab &gt; Language Level &gt; Choose Level\nFile &gt; Project Structure &gt; Modules &gt; Dependencies Tab &gt; Module SDK &gt; Choose Version</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>In Pom.xml under properties change to your version</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<pre><code>&lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;java.version&gt;16&lt;/java.version&gt;\n&lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Right Click Pom then Mavem then Reload Project</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
