    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 48,
    "last_activity_date" : 1706101372,
    "last_edit_date" : 1706101372,
    "creation_date" : 1629451138,
    "answer_id" : 68859868,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<blockquote>\n<p>Maven Projects -  and Project Structure[imported as maven in IntelliJ]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Try - If any of below pom entries present - values should be same at java level</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;java.version&gt;16&lt;/java.version&gt;\n&lt;maven.compiler.source&gt;16&lt;/maven.compiler.source&gt;\n&lt;maven.compiler.target&gt;16&lt;/maven.compiler.target&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<ol>\n<li>Project Structure -&gt; Project language level</li>\n<li>Module            -&gt; Language level</li>\n</ol>\n<hr />\n<hr />\n<blockquote>\n<p>GRADLE projects</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Since we started working with GRADLE,</p>\n<p>Build.gradle: - even below line didn't help</p>\n<pre><code>sourceCompatibility = '16'\n</code></pre>\n<p>I am getting this ERROR most of the time and Solution is\nChange <code>Gradle JVM</code> to XX</p>\n<p>Preferences | Build, Execution, Deployment | Build Tools | Gradle -&gt; JVM\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/oJF8X.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/oJF8X.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3811110,
      "reputation" : 13,
      "user_id" : 3161918,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/83a5237515d1547eba74c81603fdbee6?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Samad",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3161918/samad"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1640631082,
    "last_edit_date" : 1640631082,
    "creation_date" : 1640630560,
    "answer_id" : 70499264,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was able to overcome this issue only clearing/removing the VM configuration.\nBut you should do all the following checks:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>Menu File/Project Structure/Project (select the SDK and the correct language level -- in may case 1.8.0_201 and &quot;8 - Lambdas...&quot;)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Menu File/Project Structure/Modules/Sources (on the right) - Select the same Language Level</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Menu File/Project Structure/Dependencies (also on the right) - Select the same Module SDK</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>(If still does not work...) Menu Run/Edit configurations</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/FPr12.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/FPr12.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p>I removed the lines from the configuration and all start running.</p>\n<pre><code>--module-path\n${PATH_TO_FX}\n--add-modules\njavafx.controls,javafx.fxml\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1192412,
      "reputation" : 285,
      "user_id" : 1164888,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/1f64f6915b700d19083eaa7d60ce6ef2?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "MuhammetK",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1164888/muhammetk"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1667383888,
    "creation_date" : 1667383888,
    "answer_id" : 74287508,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>After I changed everything mentioned in answer, it was still giving me same error.\nI had to change &quot;Use complier&quot; option from &quot;Eclipse&quot; to &quot;Javac&quot; and it solved the issue for me.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lLzxT.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lLzxT.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 8098318,
      "reputation" : 1836,
      "user_id" : 6102097,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/XAdbc.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Boney",
