    "last_activity_date" : 1680600690,
    "creation_date" : 1680600690,
    "answer_id" : 75927755,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Below process worked for me:\nFile -&gt; Project Structure -&gt; Platform Settings -&gt; SDKs -&gt; (ADD JDK Required version either from disk or download it)</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 27817545,
      "reputation" : 1,
      "user_id" : 21238619,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/VZUbj.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Smars",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/21238619/smars"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1681625700,
    "creation_date" : 1681625700,
    "answer_id" : 76026173,
    "question_id" : 46280859,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>May caused by mismatching configuration of your Maven as well as project Structure.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Re-set your project configuration.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>IntelliJ IDEA - File - Project Structure - Project Settings</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Project:</strong>\nProject language level : please select one <em>(e.g. 8 - Lambdas, type annotations etc.)</em></p>\n<p><strong>Modules:</strong>\nLanguage Level: please select one same as above. <em>(e.g. 8 - Lambdas, type annotations etc.)</em></p>\n<p><strong>Apply the setting.</strong></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Re-upgrade your Maven XML configuration.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>confirm your pom.xml file whether contains the properties configure xml code as below or not.</p>\n<p>please change the version to '8'.</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;maven.compiler.source&gt;8&lt;/maven.compiler.source&gt;\n    &lt;maven.compiler.target&gt;8&lt;/maven.compiler.target&gt;\n    &lt;project.build.sourceEncoding&gt;UTF-8&lt;/project.build.sourceEncoding&gt;\n&lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Re-load Maven Project by IDEA.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>right click pom.xml -&gt; maven -&gt; Reload project.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4528798,
      "reputation" : 11833,
      "user_id" : 3679900,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 48,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/tFAHl.png?s=256",
      "display_name" : "y2k-shubham",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3679900/y2k-shubham"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
